<BR>
<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/lii.table.html"><img src="http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/icons/logo_sm.gif" alt="LII - cornell law school"></A>
<h2>Uniform Business and Financial Laws Locator</h2>
<hr>
<p>This locator links to state statutes which correspond to Uniform Laws in the subject areas of business and finance.
<p>
<I>Locators are also available for the <a  href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/uniform/ucc.html">Uniform Commercial Code</A>, <a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/uniform/probate.html">Uniform Probate Code</A>, <a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/uniform/evidence.html">Uniform Code of Evidence</A> and <a  href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/uniform/vol9.html">uniform family, health, and matrimonial laws.</A></I>
<h3>Table of Uniform Laws Covered in This Locator</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="#arbit">Uniform Arbitration Act</A>
<li><a href="#comin">Uniform Common Interest Ownership Act</A>
<li><a href="#comtr">Uniform Common Trust Fund Act</A>
<li><a href="#condo">Uniform Condominium Act</A>
<li>Uniform Construction Lien Act (no cites)
<li><a href="#concc">Uniform Consumer Credit Code (1968 Act)</A>
<li>Uniform Consumer Sales Practices Act (no cites)
<li><a href="#custr">Uniform Custodial Trust Act</A>
<li><a href="#dectr">Uniform Deceptive Trade Practices Act (1968 Act)</A>
<li><a href="#inctx">Uniform Division of Income for Tax Purposes Act</A>
<li>Uniform Dormant Mineral Interests Act (no cites)
<li>Model Employment Termination Act (no cites)
<li><a href="#fedln">Uniform Federal Lien Registration Act</A>
<li>Uniform Federal Tax Lien Registration Act (no cites)
<li><a href="#fiduc">Uniform Fiduciaries Act</A>
<li>Uniform Franchise and Business Opportunities Act (no cites)
<li><a href="#frcon">Uniform Fraudulent Conveyance Act</A>
<li><a href="#frtra">Uniform Fraudulent Transfer Act</A>
<li><a href="#lndsa">Model Land Sales Practices Act</A>
<li>Uniform Land Security Interest Act
<li><a href="#infnd">Uniform Management of Institutional Funds Act</A>
<li><a href="#print">Uniform Principal and Income Act (1962 Act)</A>
<li>Model Real Estate Cooperative Act (no cites)
<li>Model Real Estate Time-Share Act (no cites)
<li><a href="#trtax">Uniform Reciprocal Transfer Tax Act</A>
<li><a href="#lndtn">Uniform Residential Landlord and Tenant Act</A>
<li><a href="#secur">Uniform Securities Act (1956 Act)</A>
<li><a href="#sectr">Uniform Act for Simplification of Fiduciary Security Transfers</A>
<li><a href="#atrst">Uniform State Antitrust Act</A>
<li><a href="#sptrs">Uniform Supervision of Trustees for Charitable Purposes Act</A>
<li><a href="#trpwr">Uniform Trustees' Powers Act</A>
<li>Uniform Trusts Act (no cites)
</ul>
