<H1>Info Source - News &amp; Announcements</H1>

<DL>

<DT><EM><STRONG>January 26, 1996</STRONG></EM></DT>

<DD>The <a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.qlsys.ca/TBS/Info_Source/ise2001.html">Sources of

Federal Government Information</A> and the

<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.qlsys.ca/TBS/Info_Source/iee2001.html">Sources of Federal

Employee Information</A> searchable   databases have now been updated to
include

the 1995-96   material.</DD>

<DT><EM><STRONG>December 7, 1995</STRONG></EM></DT>

<DD>The Federal Regulatory Plan searchable database has now been updated to

include the 1996 Plan.  The Plan is prepared by  the Treasury Board
Secretariat.

 It provides brief descriptions  of all regulatory initiatives planned by the

government for  1996, including new regulations as well as amendments to

existing ones.</DD>

<DT><EM><STRONG>August 29, 1995</STRONG></EM></DT>

<DD>The December 1994 issue of &quot;<a  href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.qlsys.ca/TBS/Info_Source/Bulletin17e.html">Info Source

Bulletin</A>&quot; (Number 17) has now been added to Info Source Online.</DD>

</DL>

<DL>

<DT><EM><STRONG>May 15, 1995</STRONG></EM></DT>

<DD>The <a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.qlsys.ca/TBS/Info_Source/ise2001.html">Sources of

Federal Government Information</A> and the

<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.qlsys.ca/TBS/Info_Source/iee2001.html">Sources of Federal

