<DT><EM><STRONG>March 7, 1994</STRONG></EM></DT>

<DD>We have completed the design of the Online Service for easy and fast access

to the <STRONG>Info Source</STRONG> databases.  <STRONG>Info Source</STRONG>

makes it easy to find out about the Government of Canada, its organization and

Information Holdings.  It is a full text retrieval system.</DD>

