<STRONG>Info Source</STRONG> Online Service.  The Plan is prepared by the

Treasury Board Secretariat.  It provides brief descriptions of all regulatory

initiatives planned by the government for 1994, including new regulations as

well as amendments to existing ones.  It also includes a progress report on the

1993 initiatives.  To access the 1994

<EM>Federal Regulatory Plan</EM>, select number 7 from the <STRONG>Info Source

</STRONG> Main Menu.</DD></DL>

