<HTML><HEAD>
<TITLE>Supreme Court's 1995-96 Term</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY>

<!-- Any HTML can be put in here for the header -->
<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/"><img BORDER=1 src="/Link4.gif"></a>
<BR>
<ADDRESS><I>August 15, 1996</I>
</ADDRESS><H3>Important Decisions of the Supreme Court's 1995-96 Term
</H3><P>In the term concluded in <a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/supct/supct.july.1996.html">July</A>
the Supreme Court handed down decisions with full opinion in 75 cases.  All have been added to party name tables in the
<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/supct/index.html">LII Supreme Court collection</A>.  In addition,
LII editors have added available print citations to their records in this
site's searchable index to decisions of the Court and updated <a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/supct/justices/fullcourt.html">the decision lists for the Court's
nine justices</A>.
P>Signficant among this past term's decisions were the following:
<UL><LI>Involving Federal Authority
<UL><LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/supct/cases/95-754.html">Medtronic v. Lohr</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/supct/cases/94-12.html">Seminole Tribe v. Florida</A>
<BR> - <a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/uscode/25/ch29.html">Indian Gaming
Regulatory Act</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/supct/cases/94-1614.html">Wisconsin
v. New York</A>
</UL><LI>Dealing with Discrimination and Affirmative Action
<UL><LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/supct/cases/94-1039.html">Romer v. Evans</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/supct/cases/94-1941.html">United States v. Virginia</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/supct/cases/94-805.html">Bush v. Vera</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/supct/cases/94-923.html">Shaw v. Hunt</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/supct/cases/95-354.html">O'Conner v. Consolidated Coin Caterers</A>
<BR> - <a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/uscode/29/621.html">Age Discrimination in
Employment Act of 1967</A>
