<Head><Title>Cornell Law Library Guide</Title></Head>
<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF">

<!-- Any HTML can be put in here for the header -->
<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/"><img BORDER=1 src="/Link4.gif"></a>
<BR>


<center><H1>Cornell Law Library Guide</H1></center> 
<P><hr>
<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/admit/img0009.gif"><IMG
SRC="http://www.law.cornell.edu/admit/im0009sm.gif" ALIGN=bottom></A><p>

The Law Library's collection consists of close to
550,000 volumes (books and microform equivalents). 
 It is the third largest library collection on the Cornell 
campus and twentieth largest law school library in the country.
<P>

The entire Law Library staff strives to meet the library needs of the 
Cornell legal community--to acquire information and to make it available 
to readers. Please consult any staff member at the Circulation or 
Reference Desk for assistance.
<P>

<UL>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/library/gdhistory.html">History of the Library</A> 
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/library/gdhours.html">Hours</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/library/phonenos.html">Telephone Numbers</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/library/Quickinfo.html">Quick Information</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/library/Rulesregs.html">Rules and Regulations</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/library/gdfindmat.html">How to Find Materials</A>
