<P>

<HR SIZE=4><FONT SIZE=+3><STRONG>CBA Newsletters</STRONG></FONT><HR SIZE=4>
<P>
</center>
Download a copy of Adobe Acrobat Amber Reader <a href ="ftp://ftp.adobe.com/pub/adobe/Applications/Acrobat/Windows/Amber/AMBR16A2.EXE"> for Windows 3.1</A>, <a href="ftp://ftp.adobe.com/pub/adobe/Applications/Acrobat/Windows/Amber/AMBR32A2.EXE"> for Windows 95</A> (<EM>Netscape Navigator</EM>  version 2.0 or higher necessary), a copy of <a href ="ftp://ftp.adobe.com/pub/adobe/Acrobat/Macintosh/ACROREAD.MAC.hqx">Adobe Acrobat Reader</A>, MacIntosh version or the new Adobe Acrobat <a href="ftp://ftp.adobe.com/pub/adobe/Acrobat/Macintosh/Amber/ACROREAD.MAC.HQX">Amber Reader</A> for Macintosh (Netscape Navigator 2.0 and MacOS 7.0 or later necessary), in order to read the following documents.
<H4>To download and launch Adobe Acrobat Reader from Netscape Navigator browser, <a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.algonquinc.on.ca:80/cba/acrob.html">click here</A>...</H4>

<FONT SIZE=+1>

<img  hspace=10 align=left src  ="http://www.algonquinc.on.ca:80/cba/franco/gifr/acroread.gif" alt="[Acrobat icon]">  <a href ="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.algonquinc.on.ca:80/cba/aborig.pdf">Aboriginal Writes - November 1996, Vol. 2 - No. 2</A><BR>
<FONT SIZE=-1>Produced by CBA National Aboriginal Law Section</FONT><P>

<img  hspace=10 align=left src  ="http://www.algonquinc.on.ca:80/cba/franco/gifr/acroread.gif" alt="[Acrobat icon]">  <a href ="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.algonquinc.on.ca:80/cba/addmarch.pdf">Addendum - March 1996</A><BR>
<FONT SIZE=-1>Produced by CBA Communications</FONT><P>

<img hspace=10 align=left src  ="http://www.algonquinc.on.ca:80/cba/franco/gifr/acroread.gif" alt="[Acrobat icon]"> <a href ="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.algonquinc.on.ca:80/cba/updadm.pdf">Administrative Law Update - March 1996</a><BR>
<FONT SIZE=-1>Produced by the CBA National Administrative Law Section</font>
<P>
