<td><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/library/countries2.html"><IMG alt="Countries" border=0
SRC="2c.gif"></A></td>
<td><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/library/internat.html"><IMG alt="International" border=0
