<HTML>

<HEAD> <TITLE>Cornell Law Library in a Nutshell </TITLE> </HEAD>

<BODY>

<!-- Any HTML can be put in here for the header -->
<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/"><img BORDER=1 src="/Link4.gif"></a>
<BR>
 <h3>Cornell Law Library in a Nutshell</h3><hr> Located in the
heart of the Law School, the Cornell Law Library provides access to
well- organized collections and a variety of library services.  The
Library combines the strengths of a large print collection of legal
research materials with broad access to computer-based information
resources.   With close to 550,000 volumes (books and microforms
equivalents), and access to electronic information sources from a large
number of computer terminals in the library, computer area and faculty
and staff offices, the Library is a major academic research law
library, designed for the educational needs of law students and
scholarly pursuits of faculty and other legal researchers, and staffed
by a strong team of twenty three.<p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/library/vision.html">Vision</A>
<li><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/library/collection.html">Collections</A><ul>
<li><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/library/collection.html#general">The General Collection</A>
<li><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/library/collection.html#rare">The Rare Book Collection</A>
<li><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/library/collection.html#trials">The Trials Collection</A>
<li><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/library/collection.html#electronic">The Electronic
Library</A></ul></ul><p>
[<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/library/default.html">To the Cornell Law Library Homepage</A>]





