<title>Multilaterals Project</title>

<!-- Any HTML can be put in here for the header -->
<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/"><img BORDER=1 src="/Link4.gif"></a>
<BR>
<img alt="Multilaterals project" src=http://www.tufts.edu:80/fletcher/gifs/multi_hd.gif><p>
<center>
<table border=0 width=85%><TR><TD>
<FONT SIZE=2>The Multilaterals Project, begun in 1992, is an 
ongoing project designed to make available the texts of 
international multilateral conventions and other instruments. 
<a href="#About">About the Multilaterals Project</a></FONT>
</TD></TR></TABLE>
</center><p>
  

