<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Supreme Court's 1994-95 Term</TITLE></HEAD><BODY>

<!-- Any HTML can be put in here for the header -->
<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/"><img BORDER=1 src="/Link4.gif"></a>
<BR>
<address><I>July 21, 1995</I></address>
<H3>Important Decisions of the Supreme Court's 1994-95 Term</H3>
<P>In the term now concluded (<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/supct/supct.june.1995.html">with the decisions of June 29</A>) the Supreme Court handed down decisions with full opinion in 82 cases.  All have been added to party name tables in the <a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/supct/supct.table.html">LII Supreme Court collection</A>.  In addition, LII editors have added available print citations to their records in this site's searchable index of opinions and have up-dated <a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu:80/supct/justices/fullcourt.html">the decision lists for the Court's nine justices</A>.<P>Signficant among this past term's decisions were the following:
<UL>
<LI>Striking Down Federal Statutes on Constitutional Grounds
<UL>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+1121+and+plaut">Plaut v. Spendthrift Farm</A> (<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/constitution/constitution.articleiii.html">Separation of Powers - Article III</A>)
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+1260+and+lopez">United States v. Lopez</A> (<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/constitution/constitution.articlei.html#section8">Commerce Clause)
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+1631+and+rubin">Rubin v. Coors Brewing Co.</A> (<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/constitution/constitution.billofrights.html#amendmenti">First Amendment</A>)
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+1170+and+employees">United States v. National Treasury Employees Union</A> (<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/constitution/constitution.billofrights.html#amendmenti">First Amendment</A>)
</UL>
<LI>Striking Down a State Statute on Constitutional Grounds
<UL>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+1456+and+thornton">U.S. Term Limits v. Thornton</A> (<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/constitution/constitution.articlei.html">Congressional Qualifications Provisions - Article I</A>)
</UL>
<LI>Dealing with Discrimination and Affirmative Action
<UL>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+1841+and+adarand">Adarand Constructors, Inc. v. Pena</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+1543+and+mckennon">McKennon v. Nashville Banner Publishing Co.</A> (<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/29/ch14.html">Age Discrimination in Employment Act</A>)
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?94+and+631+and+miller">Miller v. Johnson</A> (<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/42/ch20.html">Voting Rights Act</A>)
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+1823+and+jenkins">Missouri v. Jenkins</A>
</UL>
<LI>Concerning <a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/constitution/constitution.billofrights.html#amendmenti">First Amendment</A> Issues
<UL>
<LI>Religion
<UL>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?94+and+780+and+capitol">Capitol Square Review &amp; Advisory Bd. v. Pinette</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?94+and+329+and+rosenberger">Rosenberger v. University of Virginia</A>
</UL>
<LI>Speech
<UL>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?94+and+226+and+florida">Florida Bar v. Went for It, Inc.</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?94+and+749+and+hurley">Hurley v. Irish-American Gay, Lesbian &amp; Bisexual Group of Boston</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+986+and+mcintyre">McIntyre v. Ohio Elections Commission</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+1631+and+rubin">Rubin v. Coors Brewing Co.</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+1170+and+employees">United States v. National Treasury Employees Union</A>
</UL>
</UL>
<LI>Concerning <a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/constitution/constitution.billofrights.html#amendmentiv">Fourth Amendment</A> Issues
<UL>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+1660+and+evans">Arizona v. Evans</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?94+and+590+and+acton">Vernonia School District v. Acton</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?94+and+5707+and+wilson">Wilson v. Arkansas</A>
</UL>
<LI>Involving <a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/constitution/constitution.amendmentxiv.html">Due Process</A>, Criminal Prosecutions and Appeals
<UL>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+7927+and+kyles">Kyles v. Whitley</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+7407+and+mcaninch">O'Neal v. McAninch</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+1911+and+sandin">Sandin v. Conner</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+7901+and+schlup">Schlup v. Delo</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+723+and+video">United States v. X-Citement Video, Inc.</A>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?94+and+6187+and+witte">Witte v. United States</A>
</UL>
<LI>Dealing with Commercial Law Issues
<UL>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+1286+and+wolens">American Airlines, Inc. v. Wolens</A> (Airline Deregulation Act)
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+1612+and+nationsbank">Nationsbank of North Carolina v. Variable Annuity Life Insurance Co.</A> (<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/12/ch2.html">National Bank Act</A>)
</UL>
<LI>Involving Intellectual Property
<UL>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?93+and+1577+and+qualitex">Qualitex v. Jacobsen Products</A> (<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/15/ch22.html">Lanham Trademark Act</A>)
</UL>
<LI>Dealing with Environmental Law
<UL>
<LI><a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/syllabi?94+and+859+and+babbitt">Babbitt v. Sweet Home Chapter of Communities for a Greater Oregon</A> (<a href="http://www.mcbinch.com/cgi-bin/mcbinch/nph-mcb?url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/16/ch35.html">Endangered Species Act</A>)
</UL>
</UL>

























