<a href="qt_h.htm #HOMOSEXUALITY">Homosexuality</a><br>
<a href="qt_h.htm #HOPE">Hope</a><br>
<a href="qt_h.htm #HUMAN POTENTIAL">Human Potential</a><br>
<a href="qt_h.htm #HUMANITY">Humanity</a><br>
<a href="qt_h.htm #HUMILITY">Humility</a><br>
<a href="qt_h.htm #HUMOR">Humor</a><br>
<a href="qt_h.htm #HYPOCRISY">Hypocrisy</a> <P>
