<A HREF="./books/dep/deptoc.htm"><IMG SRC="./images/depcov.gif" width=100 height=160 border=1 align=LEFT hspace=15 vspace=5></A>
<pre>
</pre>
<font size=+3><A HREF="./books/dep/deptoc.htm">How to Heal Depression</A></font><br>
<I>by</I> Harold H. Bloomfield, M.D. & Peter McWilliams<p>
<IMG SRC="./images/greenhlf.gif"><p>
<DD>More than two-thirds of the fifteen million Americans who are depressed don't know it.  One of them may be your friend, co-worker, child, parent, or spouse.<p>
<DD>One of them may even be you.<p>
<DD>If you think there's even a <I>possibility</I> you or someone you love <I>may</I> be depressed, please read this book.<p>
<DD>At least <I>glance</I> at the <A HREF="./books/dep/dep1a.htm#Symptoms of Depression">Symptoms of Depression</A><p>
<p>

Hardcover, 200 pages:  $14.95<br>
Audio Tapes, 6 tapes, read by the authors:  $15.95<br>
Paperback, 200 pages:  $5.95<br>

