http://www.mcwilliams.com:80/books/sur/sr5.htm 207.171.3.168 19970124124917 text/html 26788
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 24 Jan 1997 12:48:16 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 26616
