<DOCOLDNO>IA078-000528-B029-11</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.mcwilliams.com:80/books/doit/d5f.htm 207.171.3.168 19970124153305 text/html 10743
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 24 Jan 1997 15:32:04 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
