</TR>
<TR>
	<TD></TD>
	<TD><A HREF="312.htm">Suicide and Assisted Suicide</A></TD>
</TR>
<TR>
	<TD></TD>
	<TD><A HREF="313.htm">The Titanic Laws: Public Drunkenness, Loitering,<br>Vagrancy, Seat Belts, Motorcycle Helmets,<br>Public Nudity, Transvestism</A></TD>
</TR>
<TR>
	<TD VALIGN=TOP><B>PART IV</B></TD>
	<TD VALIGN=TOP><B>SIX CHAPTERS IN SEARCH OF A SHORTER BOOK</B></TD>
</TR>
<TR>
	<TD></TD>
	<TD><A HREF="401.htm">The Enlightenment or We Wer So Much Older Then;<br>We're Younger Than That Now</A></TD>
</TR>
<TR>
	<TD></TD>
	<TD><A HREF="402.htm">Prohibition: A Lesson in the Futility<br>(and Danger) of Prohibiting</A></TD>
</TR>
<TR>
	<TD></TD>
	<TD><A HREF="403a.htm">What Jesus and the Bible Really Said about Consensual Crimes</A><br>
	<BLOCKQUOTE>
